  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: Due to their siting, distribution across the rooftop, appearance and visibility in views from the surrounding public realm, the proposed antennas and supporting structures would appear as visually alien and discordant additions to the roof of the building within the sensitive location, cluttering the roof. This would therefore cause harm to the character and appearance of the building and streetscene and the nearby Bunhill and Finsbury Square Conservation Area and South Shoreditch Conservation Area. The proposals are therefore contrary policies D4 and HC1 of the London Plan (2021), policies DM2.1, DM2.3 and DM2.7 of the Development Management Policies (2013) and CS7, CS8 and CS9 of the guidance contained within the Urban Design Guide (2017)."
